{"tid":768002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華女遊日斥責店員唔識中文　網民鬧爆：丟臉","createTime":"2018-08-05T04:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T05:30:26.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"229b3e7587b0df0f9aff7733dbf3dc413a8ac8df","tid":768002,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=1527-m&amp;d=1533367700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3D1527-m%26d%3D1533367700&d=H%2BH9iofhkIX1AEbBqoXNxEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=938454fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=1527-m&amp;d=1533367700</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180804/photo/bkn-20180804175053536-0804_00952_001_01p.jpg?20180804182253\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180804%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180804175053536-0804_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20180804182253&h=f56b563d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國女遊客斥責日本女店員（圖）不懂中文，對方唯有以笑回應。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n不少人到外地旅遊時，都會學一兩句當地的語言傍身，以備不時之需。不過近日內地網傳一段短片，一名中國女遊客到日本的便利店時，用普通話向女店員說「飲料」，但對方因言語不通而聽不懂，未料遭女遊客斥責。短片曝光後，隨即被網民瘋傳，並狠批女子的行為「丟臉」。<br />\n<br />\n短片所見，一名操東北口音的中國女遊客走進一家便利店後，一邊開着手機拍片，一邊向女店員用中文說出「飲料」兩字，但店員根本聽不懂，只好以笑回應。未料，該名中國女遊客再度說一次「飲料」，女店員於是低頭道歉，更以日文表示，「真的很抱歉，我聽不懂」；惟該名女華客竟以輕佻的語氣斥責對方說：「欸？中國話為甚麼不會！」<br />\n<br />\n看過短片的內地網民無一不以該名女華客為恥，直斥其行為極度失禮，「在別人國家要求人人會你的母語？丟人」、「店員沒生氣，脾氣已經很好了」、「真的是丟人丟到國外去了」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180804/bkn-20180804175053536-0804_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180804%2Fbkn-20180804175053536-0804_00952_001.html&d=H%2BH9iofhkIX1AEbBqoXNxEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ed840139\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180804/bkn-20180804175053536-0804_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ffc2ef12b10fd86f52928ea726576bae06654885","tid":768002,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國雞who care<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79db0e4540aaec915cd80f39b13ca67e1dcc97c8","tid":768002,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"厲害了,我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這就是中華民族的底氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於小日本的領土上揚我國威,以報日本侵華的一箭之仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bff8706019867dfc0c730994367ab010c01999","tid":768002,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"中蟈畜重夠膽叫自己禮儀之邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48beb7f3cd4fa788f7a0cf8e5b9fd10f73693f48","tid":768002,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4bff8706019867dfc0c730994367ab010c01999","tid":768002,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"中蟈畜重夠膽叫自己禮儀之邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"中共竊國之後已經唔係好多年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a916e6a1dbae7d93a0389bcfb480e3ad1da34895","tid":768002,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"7仔